---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 13, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility · Viva Wellness Co."
  description="Viva Wellness Co.'s commitment to accessibility, the standards we target (WCAG 2.2 AA), and how to report a barrier."
>

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container legal-hero__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">· Accessibility</span>
      <h1 class="legal-hero__title">
        Built to be <span class="italic-display">used by everyone.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Healthcare information should not have barriers. Here is what we
        target, what we have done, and how to tell us when we have missed
        something.
      </p>
      <p class="legal-hero__updated">Last updated · {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="container legal-body__inner">

      <div class="legal-callout">
        <strong>Our standard.</strong>
        We target Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.2 Level AA
        across this website, the patient portal, and any documents we
        publish.
      </div>

      <h2 class="legal-h">What this means in practice</h2>
      <ul class="legal-list">
        <li>Keyboard navigation works across every interactive element, with a visible "Skip to main content" link at the top of every page</li>
        <li>Focus indicators are visible on links, buttons, and form fields (bronze outline)</li>
        <li>Color contrast meets AA on body and large text</li>
        <li>Form inputs have associated labels; required fields are announced to assistive technology</li>
        <li>Modal-style overlays (mobile menu, quiz focus mode) use the inert attribute so keyboard and screen-reader users cannot tab into hidden content</li>
        <li>Motion is reduced when the operating system reports <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code></li>
        <li>Images have alternative text where they carry meaning; decorative images are marked aria-hidden</li>
        <li>The site is responsive from 320px viewports up to ultrawide, and zooms cleanly to 200% without horizontal scrolling</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Working with our team</h2>
      <p>
        If you cannot access information or complete a task on this website
        or in our patient portal, contact us and we will provide the
        information or perform the task in a different format. We do not
        require you to use the website to become a patient.
      </p>
      <ul class="legal-list">
        <li>Email <a href="mailto:info&#64;vivawellnessco.com">info&#64;vivawellnessco.com</a></li>
        <li>Call or text <a href="tel:+17372107283">(737) 210-7283</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Report a barrier</h2>
      <p>
        Found something that does not work for you? Tell us. Send the page
        URL, what you were trying to do, what got in the way, and the
        assistive technology you use (if any). We aim to acknowledge within
        two business days and remediate or provide an alternative within
        thirty.
      </p>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:info&#64;vivawellnessco.com">info&#64;vivawellnessco.com</a>
        with "Accessibility" in the subject line.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Ongoing work</h2>
      <p>
        Accessibility is not a one-time project. We test with automated
        tools and with real assistive technology, and we re-audit at every
        major design change. If you spot a regression on a page that worked
        before, we want to hear about it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Formal complaints</h2>
      <p>
        If you believe the practice has not provided equal access to its
        services based on disability, you may file a complaint with the
        U.S. Department of Health and Human Services, Office for Civil
        Rights, under Section 1557 of the Affordable Care Act:
        <a href="https://www.hhs.gov/civil-rights/filing-a-complaint/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hhs.gov/civil-rights/filing-a-complaint</a>.
        You will not be retaliated against for filing a complaint.
      </p>

      <p class="legal-foot">
        Viva Wellness Co. · 5900 Balcones Dr #19640, Austin, TX 78731
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 11vw, 9rem) 0 clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .legal-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(800px 500px at 75% 0%, rgba(214, 134, 74, 0.14), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .legal-hero__inner { position: relative; max-width: 70ch; }
  .legal-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6.5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-hero__title .italic-display { color: var(--bronze-bright); }
  .legal-hero__updated {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mute);
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    padding-top: 1.2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .legal-body { padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem); }
  .legal-body__inner { max-width: 70ch; margin: 0 auto; }

  .legal-callout {
    background: var(--ink-2);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--bronze);
    padding: 1.6rem 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(247, 244, 238, 0.9);
  }
  .legal-callout strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bronze);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .legal-h {
    font-family: var(--font-display-italic);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.6vw, 1.9rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 2.8rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .legal-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(247, 244, 238, 0.85);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .legal-body a {
    color: var(--bronze);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(214, 134, 74, 0.4);
    transition: color 200ms var(--ease), border-color 200ms var(--ease);
  }
  .legal-body a:hover {
    color: var(--bronze-bright);
    border-color: var(--bronze-bright);
  }
  .legal-body code {
    font-family: var(--font-code);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--bronze);
    background: var(--ink-2);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .legal-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-list li {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
    color: rgba(247, 244, 238, 0.85);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .legal-list li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .legal-foot {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--mute);
  }
</style>
